00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:01,680
Made a mistake?

2
00:00:01,630 --> 00:00:03,041
Do not worry.

3
00:00:03,041 --> 00:00:10,951
Hold Control down and tap the letter Z. Control and Z together is Undo — it steps you back, one change at a time.

4
00:00:10,951 --> 00:00:12,921
Nothing here can break.

